Workout.Description: Good night if racing. My legs aren't all the way back but were getting there. 2nd in the 10 lap on a n attach from 1/2 back with 1/2 a lap left. More tactics than speed but ill take it. Second out in the miss and out, boxed out or crash: easy choice. Took a flyer in a 40 lap scratch to set team members up. Worked! Different to race with a team up there this year, not sure it's fair but it was fun to do tonight anyway. I'm going to do the rusty ride. I took the MTB for a spin with my brace on and it seemed to work.
